# test_worldgen_smoke.hms — Smoke test: does world generation complete without crashing?
#
# World generation + SAVE9.GAM creation happen in Config_Apply_And_Create_New_Game()
# BEFORE Screen_Control() is entered. By the time this scenario runs, the game is
# already at the Main Screen with a valid save file written.
#
# This scenario just tells the game to exit cleanly.
#
# Usage:
#   HeMoM --newgame test_worldgen.ini --scenario test_worldgen_smoke.hms
#
# Validation:
#   - HeMoM exits with code 0
#   - SAVE9.GAM exists and is exactly 123300 bytes

quit
